content.html: That’s where mine was at for the longest time. Tolerable. Today it saw the headset, connected, then played audio through Line Out. Manually select headset in audio. Pop OS says cool. Play music. Sound from speakers. Setting is Line Out again.
content.value:
That’s where mine was at for the longest time. Tolerable.

Today it saw the headset, connected, then played audio through Line Out. 

Manually select headset in audio. Pop OS says cool. Play music. Sound from speakers. Setting is Line Out again.
